## Tech Stack (UPDATED - Show Sophistication!)\
\
### Frontend Architecture\
- **React 18** with TypeScript for type-safe component development\
- **Radix UI + shadcn/ui** for accessible, production-ready component library\
- **TanStack Query (v5)** for sophisticated server state management and caching\
- **Wouter** for lightweight client-side routing\
- **Canvas Drawing API** for student handwritten work capture\
- **Tailwind CSS** for responsive, modern UI design\
- **Responsive Design** optimized for iPad (primary student device)\
\
### Backend Services\
- **Node.js + Express.js** with TypeScript\
- **Service-Oriented Architecture** with dependency injection (AssessmentService, QuestionManagementService, ProficiencyService, CurriculumService)\
- **Drizzle ORM** for type-safe database operations\
- **Session-Based Authentication** with PostgreSQL session store\
- **Role-Based Access Control** (Admin, Parent, Child)\
- **Express Sessions** with cookie-based authentication\
- **Multer** for file uploads (PDF, images for question processing)\
\
### Database & Storage\
- **PostgreSQL 16** via Neon serverless platform\
- **Optimized Schema** with separated proficiency tracking tables\
- **Comprehensive Data Model:** Users, children, assessments, questions, proficiency, achievements, feedback\
- **Session Persistence** with connect-pg-simple\
- **Automated Migrations** via Drizzle Kit\
\
### AI & Machine Learning\
- **Multi-Model Strategy:**\
  - **OpenAI GPT-4o-mini:** Primary question generation, learning contexts, AI enhancements\
  - **OpenAI GPT-5:** Advanced marking, mathematical reasoning, critical validation\
  - **Deepseek R1:** Secondary verification and solution generation\
  - **Google Gemini AI:** PDF OCR extraction, backup for visual questions\
- **Template-Based Visual Generation:** Deterministic math + AI enhancement for accuracy\
- **Pattern Learning Engine:** Extracts pedagogical patterns from school-verified questions\
- **Context-Aware Feedback:** OCR analysis of handwritten work with targeted explanations\
- **Emergency-Stop Safeguards:** Age-appropriate content constraints and safety architecture\
\
### Payment & Monetization\
- **Stripe Integration:** Checkout sessions, webhooks, Customer Portal\
- **Subscription Management:** Trial tracking, plan management, billing verification\
- **Feature Gating System:** Ready for subscription-based feature access\
- **Current Status:** 95% complete, operationally dormant for PMF validation\
\
### Educational Framework\
- **Singapore MOE Curriculum Standards:** Full P1-P6 coverage\
- **12 Mathematical Heuristics:** PSLE-aligned problem-solving strategies\
- **Dual-Proficiency Algorithms:** 70% sub-strand + 30% heuristic weighting\
- **Mastery-Based Progression:** Threshold-based advancement system\
- **Curriculum-Driven Decision Framework:** Visual question probability based on grade level and topic\
